    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Iun</abbr><ex>oni</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>et <expan><abbr>Gen</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> l<lb break="no" n="4"/>oci <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iuli</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Petunnati<lb break="no" n="6"/>us b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ver</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> III et <expan><abbr>Qua</abbr><ex>drato</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der linken Nebenseite stilisiertes Blitzbündel, auf der rechten Nebenseite Opfermesser und Axt. Z. 7 und 8 befinden sich auf dem Sockel. Z. 5: TI-Ligatur; Z. 8: MP-, ET-, VA-Ligaturen. Blattförmige hederae als Worttrenner, in Z. 4 dreieckige Worttrenner.</p>
            </div>
